The primary purpose of thesis statement in an essay to convey the central argument of the pieces.It serves the summary of the key idea and provide roadmap for the reader.
citing source in academic writing is important for several reason.It gives credit to the original author.It allows reader to verify your information.
A research question is aim to explore or inquire a topic while hypothesis proposes answer or explanation.
